[I] Generates an ext2 filesystem as a normal (non-root) user

[T] Genext2fs generates an ext2 filesystem as a normal (non-root) user. It
[T] does not require you to mount the image file to copy files on it, nor
[T] does it require that you become the superuser to make device nodes.

[U] https://genext2fs.sourceforge.net/

[A] Xavier Bestel <xavier.bestel@free.fr>
[M] Rene Rebe <rene@t2-project.org>

